description.en-us: The Custom Classics line was first released in 2007. The line featured models in the 1/50 scale that were highly detailed. All models came with rubber wheels that had treads. The reason this line didn't run very long is probably the over-use of some castings. Some cars were used eight times in one year. Sometimes even multiple times in a series.
